* Delta Lake
** What it is
***_ Open-source storage framework
***_ Adds transactions to data lakes
***_ Runs on Azure Data Lake Storage
** Key Features
*** ACID Transactions
****_ Atomicity, Consistency
****_ Isolation, Durability
*** Scalable Metadata
****_ Billions of files without perf loss
*** Data Versioning
****_ Time travel queries
****_ Rollback to previous states
*** Unified Processing
****_ Same table: batch + streaming
** Delta Tables
***_ Default table format in Azure Databricks
***_ SQL queries & DataFrame API
***_ All new data stored with guarantees
@endmindmap
